Stefano Corsi <ippo@madeinlinux.com> is the author of Quizzer and of the 
sample test set. He has also modified Debconf to use it as a template
system for Quizzer.

Joey Hess <joey@kitenet.net> is the author of Debconf, the library/system
used for Debian configuration.

Alessandro Briosi <abriosi@madeinlinux.com> e Giuliano Pellegrini <gpellegrini@madeinlinux.com> have created the sample quiz-long.txt.

Christopher Gabriel <cgabriel@madeinlinux.com> has contributed to the sample quiz-long.txt
